sequenceDiagram
    actor Reviewer as 裁定者
    participant API as REST API
    participant DB as 数据库

    Reviewer->>API: GET /api/reviews/{taskId}
    API->>DB: 查询所有标注员提交的标注结果
    DB-->>API: 标注结果列表
    API-->>Reviewer: {annotatorResults: [...]}

    alt 全部采纳某标注员
        Reviewer->>API: POST /api/reviews/adopt<br/>{taskId, dataId, annotatorId}
        API-->>Reviewer: {code:200, message:"裁定完成"}
    else 手动裁定
        Reviewer->>API: POST /api/reviews/manual<br/>{taskId, dataId, propositions, relations}
        API-->>Reviewer: {code:200, message:"裁定草稿已保存"}
    else 退回修改
        Reviewer->>API: POST /api/reviews/reject<br/>{taskId, dataId, userId, reason}
        API-->>Reviewer: {code:200, message:"已退回标注员重新标注"}
    end
